The '''Rianitus Period''' of history lasted from [[9000 BBY]] to [[8000 BBY]]. It was remembered for the 275-year reign of [[Blotus]] the Hutt. Around the end of this period (c. 8000 BBY), the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] established an outpost on [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare's]] eastern continent.

==Timeline of the Rianitus Period==
*c. [[9000 BBY]]
**The [[Rianitus Period]] begins.
**[[Jiroch-Reslia]] joins the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]].

*c. [[8000 BBY]]
**The [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] establishes a small outpost on Malastare's eastern continent.
**The [[Gran/Legends|Gran]] first settle on [[Malastare/Legends|Malastare]].
**[[Elrood/Legends|Elrood]] is colonized by the Republic.
**[[Goroth Prime/Legends|Goroth Prime]] is discovered by the [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorians]] and the [[Corellian/Legends|Corellians]].
**Three [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtroopers]] appear on an unidentified planet, after being transported from [[0 ABY/Legends|0 ABY]] by [[Splendid Ap]]
**The [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Clak'dor I]] is swallowed by its expanding [[Star/Legends|star]], [[Colu/Legends|Colu]].
**The [[Rianitus Period]] ends.

